ActiveQueueDefinitionWithTriggersList is a List
    propagate as a drill
    title is "ActiveNow"
    show 10 lines
    initially display search
    no data message is "NothingActiveRightNow"
        description is "<system current timestamp>_-_RefreshToUpdateThisList"
        icon is icon.icon-empty-no-orders-new
    Display Fields
        AsyncQueueDefinition
            label is "Name"
            display as tag
                color of yellow when (IsSuspended)
            sort order is primary
        Description
        MaxActiveActions
            allow update
            raise blue alert when (QueueGroupExists)
                mouse over text is "QueueGroupMaxActiveActionsIs<AsyncQueueGroup.MaxActiveActions>"
        Priority
            allow update
            sort order is ProcessQueuesSortSet
        SaveHistory
            allow update
        Suspended
            allow update
            raise yellow alert when (IsSuspended)
                mouse over text is untranslatable:"<SuspendedMessage>"
        QueueAsBindingKey
        TransNoOfQueued
            label is "Queued"
            display as tag
                color of purple
        TransNoOfActive
            label is "Active"
            display as tag
                color of blue
        TransNoOfFailed
            label is "Failed"
            raise red alert when (HasFailedTriggers)
        TransNoOfFinished
            label is "Finished"
    Instance Selection
        where (NoOfActive >  blank)
    Actions
        action is refresh
        action is Resume
            hide when invalid
            valid when (Suspended)
        action is Suspend
            hide when invalid
            valid when (not Suspended)
        action is saved searches
            hide when invalid
    Detail Sections
        Triggers
            allow nested detail sections
            list is AsyncActionTrigger set.AsyncActionTriggerByQueueList
